description:
This ring has 3 charges, and it regains 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn. While wearing the ring, you can expend 1 charge to cast one of the following spells (save DC 13) from it:
• {spell:Animal Friendship}
• {spell:Fear} (affects Beasts only)
• {spell:Speak with Animals}

This rod has the following properties.
**Alertness.** 
While holding the rod, you have Advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks and on Initiative rolls. Spells. While holding the rod, you can cast the following spells from it:
• {spell:Detect Evil and Good}
• {spell:Detect Magic}
• {spell:Detect Poison and Disease}
• {spell:See Invisibility}
**Protective Aura.** 
As a {action:Magic} action, you can plant the haft end of the rod in the ground, whereupon the rod's head sheds Bright Light in a 60-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 60 feet. While in that Bright Light, you and your allies gain a +1 bonus to Armor Class and saving throws and can sense the location of any {condition:Invisible} creature that is also in the Bright Light.
The rod's head stops glowing and the effect ends after 10 minutes or when a creature takes a {action:Magic} action to pull the rod from the ground. Once used, this property can't be used again until the next dawn.
